    {
      "id": "43",
      "name": "介绍",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "绘想游迹",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "在剧演准备间的角落里，原本空白的画布上突然浮现出了绚丽的色彩。触碰画布之时，根据触碰者的经历不同，似乎能将人传送到不同的秘境…",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "与特定的同伴一起探索画中世界，或许能将珍贵的回忆绘制成独一无二的图景。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "玩法详情",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "每个",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "绘想游迹",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "挑战关卡的主题都对应一位特定的角色。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "参与该关卡的挑战，需符合两项条件：",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "1. 该角色",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "等级",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "达到",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "90",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "级；",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "2. 该角色",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "好感度等级",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "达到",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "8",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "级。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "当符合上述条件后，将消耗2把",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 6279,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "遊跡鑰匙",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "，可以解锁1个角色的挑战关卡，后续挑战同一关卡时，将不会再次消耗钥匙。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/27/41133912/160b26d9fbc7cd327e4d7461378cb76e_8009572621343506825.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "游迹钥匙的获取方法：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "1. 旅行者初始可获得",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "2",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "把游迹钥匙。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "2. 在每一期",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 5832,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/03/142453215/3a7e2d2c12d795fbb6e6ceb679cfc0e4_3980120309767554265.png",
                      "menu_id": 14,
                      "name": "幻想真境劇詩",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "中，以",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "第6幕或更高",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "的挑战进度结算，可获得1把游迹钥匙。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "3. 在每一期",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 5832,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/03/142453215/3a7e2d2c12d795fbb6e6ceb679cfc0e4_3980120309767554265.png",
                      "menu_id": 14,
                      "name": "幻想真境劇詩",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "中，以",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "第10幕",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "的挑战进度结算，可获得1把游迹钥匙。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "完成每一期「幻想真境剧诗」演出挑战，可以领取游迹钥匙。「幻想真境剧诗」刷新时，未领取的游迹钥匙将无法保留。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "旅行者至多同时持有4把游迹钥匙，钥匙数量达到上限时，将暂时无法获得新的钥匙。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
